{"tid":242522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本：北韓飛彈高度破2千公里 疑為新飛彈","createTime":"2017-05-14T03:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T06:24:02.000Z","uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c025fa8f5fe2d9ea268d7109863043caf8c8f8e","tid":242522,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"日：北韓飛彈高度破2千公里 疑為新飛彈<br />\n<br />\n南韓軍方表示，北韓今晨從西部平安北道龜城附近，發射一不明物體，飛行約700公里，南韓軍方正蒐集情報中，應是型號不明的彈道飛彈。南韓新總統文在寅上任不到一周，這是北韓在他上任後首度試射飛彈。文在寅聽取簡報後指示召開國家安全保障會議（NSC），並表示「唯有北韓改變態度，雙方才能談對話」。<br />\n<br />\n10:45<br />\n日本防衛大臣稻田朋美表示，北韓今晨試射的飛彈，飛行高度破2000公里，有可能是新型飛彈。稻田說，推估這枚飛彈落在距離北韓東岸400公里遠的日本海。<br />\n<br />\n09:26<br />\n美軍太平洋司令部稍早也證實，偵測到北韓發射一枚飛彈，其飛行情況與洲際彈道飛彈並不一致，美軍正在進行評估。<br />\n<br />\n08:07&nbsp;<br />\n南韓聯合參謀本部表示，飛彈飛行約700公里，韓美正在進行進一步分析，韓軍正在密切關注北韓的挑釁動向，保持高度警戒。從飛行距離相當長來看，試射可能成功。平安北道的龜城距離平壤以北約100公里，北韓曾於今年2月12日在此地試射「北極星2號」中遠端彈道飛彈（IRBM）。<br />\n<br />\n05:50<br />\n日本內閣官房長官菅義偉周日早上6時半舉行緊急記者會表示，北韓於14日5時28分左右（台灣時間周日凌晨4時半左右），在西北部發射一枚彈道飛彈，飛行約30分鐘，墜落日本海，但應未落入日本專屬經濟區（EEZ）海域。日本外務省表示，準備透過外交管道提出抗議。日本海上保安廳則稱，目前尚未接獲船舶受害資訊。<br />\n<br />\n北韓4月29日曾試射飛行物，據悉僅在發射幾分鐘後空中爆炸。包括此次試射，北韓今年共7次試射飛彈。這是南韓新總統文在寅10日上任以來，北韓首次試射飛彈。文在寅對北韓偏向採取「陽光政策」，希望和北韓展開對話。由於文在寅執政後兩韓對話的可能性增大，北韓的此次試射尤為引人關注。分析認為，北韓可能意在增加談判籌碼，掌握主導權，另有分析指出，這次試射也可能是對美、韓聯合軍演嗆聲，展現不顧美國壓力的意志。而在北韓發射飛彈後，文在寅喊話稱，唯有北韓改變態度，南北韓才有可能對話。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170514/1118186/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170514%2F1118186%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=06ea2fb2\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170514/1118186/</a>"},{"pid":"9117575224dfb8984fd885e34248dafb0ef4f330","tid":242522,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"飛行高度2000公里 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c81427e26a8ea1689800e93c3eaea53b2286cf7","tid":242522,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"當侵侵無到？！<br />\n等睇核試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742b65c587e02db9a10169b3260e798742cd0466","tid":242522,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:55:18.000Z","msg":"高度破2000公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ed7f9c972b8b6af06ff2d4c33e3df5dd483175","tid":242522,"uid":33676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:07:53.000Z","msg":"出左地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ec2c5f80d8c17fea568c45f8b5225e38ec2988","tid":242522,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"射啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76bf5c640f4c5e3f315e47266f762a2e5aeae75f","tid":242522,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"地球半徑6371公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5636c8107d35e017d306c9e672191b2942a4d81a","tid":242522,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:11:16.000Z","msg":"感謝支那提供技術"},{"pid":"812e16caeede850568758559b0f7293562d7ef4c","tid":242522,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"射爆支那"},{"pid":"4e601a33bb2854752f45ed0901627bfc80a04717","tid":242522,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/121907_654b227439b102dbf9f19771030aef54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F121907_654b227439b102dbf9f19771030aef54.jpg&h=5109fd34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13540ebd98455a9374ee28eb93e13189137a9d2f","tid":242522,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:20:15.000Z","msg":"北韓科技真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434736587a2b7bd476e12159fa593d7dcfac7bea","tid":242522,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽到厭"},{"pid":"c5e9db4b54d09e1d1a0d9787ff84b351bbc429b5","tid":242522,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高度破2000公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n稲田防衛相：北朝鮮のミサイル、高度2000キロ超に達した<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n［東京　１４日　ロイター］ - 稲田朋美防衛相は１４日、同日早朝に北朝鮮が発射したミサイルについて、高度２０００キロ超に達したことを明らかにした。北朝鮮のミサイルの<span style=\"color: red;\">高度が２０００キロを超えたのは初めて</span>。稲田防衛相は、飛距離が約８００キロ、飛行時間が約３０分間だったことと合わせ、新型ミサイルの可能性があるとした。<br />\n<br />\n＊記事の詳細はこの後送信します。新しい記事には見出しに「ＵＰＤＡＴＥ」と表示します。 (久保信博<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/jp.mobile.reuters.com/article/amp/idJPL4N1IG007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fjp.mobile.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Famp%2FidJPL4N1IG007&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ba27f4c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/jp.mobile.reuters.com/article/amp/idJPL4N1IG007</a>"},{"pid":"65cdf87d5120d3f9136c991c21b4ca2b5797da21","tid":242522,"uid":27363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:30:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/121907_654b227439b102dbf9f19771030aef54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F121907_654b227439b102dbf9f19771030aef54.jpg&h=5109fd34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥仔金終於可以打飛機射粒近地衞星落嚟玩下喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f811f6bb012a4e42e90b3565c121dcfdc36851","tid":242522,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"有時都唔知金仔諗乜<br />\n文在寅話要廢薩德<br />\n佢就第二日試射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b18cd771c7da41cf8ebf4d86efaf195be80016","tid":242522,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時都唔知金仔諗乜<br />\n文在寅話要廢薩德<br />\n佢就第二日試射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n北泡遲早變成為軍事強國 <br />\n統一朝鮮不是夢"},{"pid":"83ba3f4613f36363f80b7bb6ff2c1f8459f41985","tid":242522,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時都唔知金仔諗乜<br />\n文在寅話要廢薩德<br />\n佢就第二日試射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係今日特登賀一賀習種狗乜一戴一露"},{"pid":"137800bfc44b7ed6a3aa9a823d1a6bc1e3513eca","tid":242522,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:16:51.000Z","msg":"兩千公里 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n射出太空再返黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9548a907b0a1bf7910e9ea2c490be8ba1412f579","tid":242522,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shockin